{"tid":1130531,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"一齊討論吓周國賢大碟<仲間>","createTime":"2019-04-29T06:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T03:04:51.000Z","uid":108351,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"137b2dfbc72ef2e97afcadbc5422b45751480222","tid":1130531,"uid":108351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:11:44.000Z","msg":"01 去他***的世界 4:24<br />\n曲 周國賢 // 詞 林若寧<br />\n<br />\n02 錢七 3:23<br />\n曲 Goro Wong // 詞 藍奕邦<br />\n<br />\n03 鬼才 3:24<br />\n曲 貝祖貽 // 詞 藍奕邦<br />\n<br />\n04 橡筋 4:44<br />\n曲 周國賢 // 詞 李倩菱<br />\n<br />\n05 凡夫的樂章 4:55<br />\n曲 周國賢 // 詞 李倩菱<br />\n<br />\n06 黑歷史 3:05<br />\n曲 周國賢 // 詞 林若寧、陳煩、林菲<br />\n<br />\n07 鑿壁偷光 2:54<br />\n曲 周國賢 // 詞 陳心遙<br />\n<br />\n08 守口如瓶 3:23<br />\n曲 藍奕邦 // 詞 藍奕邦<br />\n<br />\n09 The Flux Capacitor - Instrumental 15:09<br />\n曲 周國賢<br />\n<br />\n10 Shine Like A Star - Hidden Track 3:07<br />\n曲 周國賢 // 詞 周國賢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d2u6RUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd2u6RUE.jpg&h=3f8505f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17b4c4653af1d6151f8ec49e1a3b5a1e3fc6a618","tid":1130531,"uid":108351,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:13:45.000Z","msg":"大碟主題及連貫性/完整度<br />\n<br />\n仲間呢隻碟係講緊周國賢同佢嘅戰友，所以都見到佢喺呢隻碟入面有多咗同其他音樂人嘅collaboration - 高佬寫錢七嘅曲、邦邦包辦守口如瓶嘅曲詞、Joey Pui / ANWIYCTI 製作鬼才。不過覺得有部分歌好似扣題不足，好似係橡筋、黑歷史、守口如瓶（定係邦邦真係暗戀周爸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）咁，似乎係講情愛關係多於周爸同佢嘅仲間嘅關係。如果可以扣題多啲隻碟就會更完整。<br />\n<br />\n歌曲質素<br />\n<br />\n可以話每一首都係佳作。歌曲亦都涉獵到唔同種類，而去他***的世界同鬼才可以話係繼灰人同消化不良之後再挑戰大家口味。編曲方面都相當有心，尤其係喺上述兩首歌都見到編曲越來越複雜同有層次，而歌與歌之間嘅連貫都好smooth (所以聽呢隻碟唔好shuffle)，例如個人覺得錢七自己本身好好&quot;un&quot;，而01-03連住咁聽仲好&quot;un&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\nThe Flux Capacitor // Shine Like A Star<br />\n<br />\nThe Flux Capacitor係Back to the Future入面嘅時光機嘅core component（其實我都冇睇過套戲，只係google過），而首歌重複咗幾次守口如瓶入面兩句嘅旋律。如果有睇錢七同守口如瓶MV就會知入面架車係時光機，所以聽完The Flux Capacitor就象徵過咗一個time travel。咁點解要time travel呢...唔知大家聽唔聽得出Shine Like A Star係寫比邊個？細佬聽完Shine Like A Star之後聽光/光之外就好有feel喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"1b593326f918602d63c49eb6357084acee4685eb","tid":1130531,"uid":108351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:15:51.000Z","msg":"細佬第一次寫碟評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />寫得唔好大家請見諒"},{"pid":"a81d41fbc0f8d174361b2e81394e4712bb8e15f6","tid":1130531,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:19:01.000Z","msg":"碟鋪未出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d640e417b8c525a8b6fa3da5a36d3faaedd814dd","tid":1130531,"uid":108351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a81d41fbc0f8d174361b2e81394e4712bb8e15f6","tid":1130531,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:19:01.000Z","msg":"碟鋪未出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:27:45.000Z","msg":"好似話今日出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/29/142659_1ad76bbaf89d3bf1cec6552c27b51ba3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F29%2F142659_1ad76bbaf89d3bf1cec6552c27b51ba3.png&h=661358a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcd408051773df8fde82dc68034f3ff4b359dcfa","tid":1130531,"uid":163953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:51:23.000Z","msg":"覺得黑歷史，橡筋同守口係為咗湊齊啲歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />btw,啲歌一開始唔多入耳，但聽多次就好有feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c45ad8a8b1812974a07ad4dc6c9ddc8eb01fc25","tid":1130531,"uid":108351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcd408051773df8fde82dc68034f3ff4b359dcfa","tid":1130531,"uid":163953,"like":1,